</item>
<item>
 <title>SDS add-on to Support Plan</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-add-support-plan</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS add-on to Support Plan is for people with mental health problems and their supporters.
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SDS add-on to Support Plan helps people with mental health problems to plan in advance for how they will manage their SDS when their condition fluctuates and they become unwell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS add–on to Support Plan can be used as an extension to assessment and support planning (WRAP is an option) to plan and record an SDS advance directive.
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
 <pubDate>Fri, 09 Jan 2015 14:22:38 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>admin_pilotlight</dc:creator>
